node.text: Yes!!!! It’s official. I’m opening a restaurant!!!! But I’m learning…NO MORE SPENDING MY OWN MONEY!!!! I’ve learned credit is KING (or Queen). If I can offer any advise to you all it’s get your credit right!!! You don’t want to be staring opportunities in the face and you can’t move forward because you have made bad decisions with your credit. The good thing is it’s not too late to fix it. Hit up @mikethecreditchamp and he’ll get you right. Get negative items removed. Boost your credit score, clean up your past and get started on your future!

node.text: These two have been using it well before we released it to the public and said they wanted to be the faces of the brand. I told them they’d have to shoot videos. Notice all the personality when they think the cameras are just recording a “practice” shot. The minute they think it’s the real deal they get all shy and weird acting. I was cracking up inside! Overall I think they did a great job when they finally got it together. Show Marques and @lilmendc some love on their first @yelleskincare FRESH START VIDEO! If you’re a teen and you got what it takes to be a Face of Yelle Fresh Start, Get the system and tag me on your videos. I can’t wait to post them on my page!

node.text:
You’re gonna go through some stuff. The key is to deal with the issues head on, love through it sometimes tough lessons some times easier lessons, bounce back and still love and take care of eachother. Family is a two way street. We are all learning how to love each other. Omere’s needs are different from Skylars who’s are different from Infinity and Aasim’s or Lil Mendeecees. Through trial and error we learn how to love each individual person and hope that child loves us back the way we need to be loved as a parent. #1 fact is as parents we want to love and help our children overcome emotional obstacles and embrace their worth in
order to reach their full potential. Strong, stable and secure kids  are not born, they’re raised! (My mission statement for EGL PUD is true in my house too) Tune In TONIGHT! 8pm on VH1 @loveandhiphop @vh1 
.
Here’s a little behind the scenes of what my house was like a few weeks after we shot the show. Families heal. Families grow. That’s all I pray for. Constant healing, understanding and growth♥️

With love,
Yandy

node.text: Yes!!!! It’s official. I’m opening a restaurant!!!! But I’m learning…NO MORE SPENDING MY OWN MONEY!!!! I’ve learned credit is KING (or Queen). If I can offer any advise to you all it’s get your credit right!!! You don’t want to be staring opportunities in the face and you can’t move forward because you have made bad decisions with your credit. The good thing is it’s not too late to fix it. Hit up @mikethecreditchamp and he’ll get you right. Get negative items removed. Boost your credit score, clean up your past and get started on your future!

Can you believe this will be our 5th Pop Up in Atlanta! We appreciate all your support immensely! The next one will go down on Saturday, August 28th and will commemorate the End Of Summer! So don’t miss our last Pop Up of the Summer! 

To Register, send an intro of your brand/products pics and links to 
TheBigBlackPopUp@Gmail.com (please check the spelling). Registration correspondence will be completed in the order they are received. 
For Returnees, you know what to do! 

We are ending the Summer with a BANG! DJ,’s, Food Trucks, beautiful people, and of course, our VENDORS! 

Location: 
…..
Yelle Skin Care (Outside) 
55 Upper Alabama St Atlanta, GA 30303
Make sure you follow 👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾 @TheBigBlackPopUp 🛍

node.text: These two have been using it well before we released it to the public and said they wanted to be the faces of the brand. I told them they’d have to shoot videos. Notice all the personality when they think the cameras are just recording a “practice” shot. The minute they think it’s the real deal they get all shy and weird acting. I was cracking up inside! Overall I think they did a great job when they finally got it together. Show Marques and @lilmendc some love on their first @yelleskincare FRESH START VIDEO! If you’re a teen and you got what it takes to be a Face of Yelle Fresh Start, Get the system and tag me on your videos. I can’t wait to post them on my page!

✨ Fresh Start Milk & Honey Cleanser:Made with Coconut Milk, Natural Honey Gel, Infused with Papaya Enzymes, Apricot Kernel Oil & Vitamin E.
